dev.marksman.kraftwerk

Class SizeParameters

  • java.lang.Object
    • dev.marksman.kraftwerk.SizeParameters

  • public final class SizeParameters
extends java.lang.Object
    Guidelines for choosing sizes.

    Generators will consult these parameters when tasked with creating objects that have sizes (e.g. collections).
